=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09Eight days after dispatching Timothy McVeigh, the United States=
 carried out=20
its second federal execution. Unlike McVeigh, Juan Raul Garza, a drug=20
trafficker and murderer, had apologised for his crimes.
=09=09=09=09
=09=09=09=09The United States Justice Department said it would try to settl=
e a=20
long-running civil lawsuit against the tobacco industry that was filed in=
=20
1999 in an attempt to recover billions of dollars spent on tobacco-related=
=20
illnesses.
