=09=09=09=09In Bulgaria=01,s general election, a movement headed by ex-King=
 Simeon II won=20
half of the 240 seats in parliament. An ethnic-Turkish party said it was=20
ready to join a coalition. It is unclear whether Simeon will become prime=
=20
minister, seek the presidency in the autumn or call the shots from behind t=
he=20
scenes.
