=09=09=09=09After Tony Blair=01,s post-electoral reshaping of Britain=01,s =
administration, his=20
chancellor of the exchequer (finance minister), Gordon Brown, announced new=
=20
measures to bash cartels, encourage entrepreneurs and speed up land-use=20
planning decisions. No, the relevant ministries have not been abolished.
